{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"2523dbc2e1","title":"关于锡好工作的训令","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"3de4ffd6bd","index":0,"year":1939,"month":6,"day":24,"articleId":"2523dbc2e1"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji13","name":"毛泽东全集第13卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji13.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji13":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"4d1a46db90","type":"paragraph","text":"关于锡好工作的训令“","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji13","articleId":"2523dbc2e1"},{"id":"7ac0d2dbe8","type":"paragraph","text":"（1939年6月24日）在目前形势下敌探好细与反共分子对我军的破坏工作一定积极化，并且他们可能相互结合。因此锡好工作的重要性大为增加，我们必须用新的注意力对付新的阴谋破坏，从认识上、组织上以至技术上，改变到适合新的情况，这是当前好工作的总方向。[1]这是毛泽东和王骤祥、谭政、吴溉之对八路军新图军各部发出的关于锈师工作的训令。","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji13","articleId":"2523dbc2e1"}],"page":{"id":"ef737bc01b","publicationId":"maoquanji13","articleId":"2523dbc2e1","start":467,"end":467}}}},"__N_SSG":true}